Image:Elizabeth Olsen TIFF 2011.jpg|thumb|Elizabeth Olsen in 2011
Elizabeth Olsen (born February 16, 1989) is an American musician and actress. She was born in Los Angeles, California. She is the sister of the actresses Mary-Kate and Ashley Olsen. She is most known for her role as the Red Witch in the Marval Comic Universe. She has acted in her sisters' movies, and in other movies.
